WEBVTT

00:00:00.710 --> 00:00:02.532
MR. DAVID ROSENFELD,

00:00:03.487 --> 00:00:09.187
ir hot geredt fun, mir zenen, ir hot dertseylt fun nayntsn eyn un fertsik,

00:00:09.187 --> 00:00:12.465
ven di ungern zenen arayngekumen in SEVLUS.

00:00:12.791 --> 00:00:15.091
nu vos iz demolst pasirt?

00:00:16.140 --> 00:00:19.662
ACTUALLY zenen di ungern arayngekumen in akht un draysik

00:00:19.702 --> 00:00:20.581
yo.

00:00:21.562 --> 00:00:22.676
un,

00:00:24.158 --> 00:00:28.514
un un efsher shoyn, un... ven ikh hob gevoynt in Selish,

00:00:29.015 --> 00:00:31.989
iz bay mi-, bay mir un mayn vayb olehasholem

00:00:32.094 --> 00:00:33.796
geborn gevorn tsvey kinder.

00:00:34.743 --> 00:00:38.474
dos eltste kind, der hot geheysn geheysn, di yidishe nomen iz Leye,

00:00:38.989 --> 00:00:41.018
me hot zi gerufn Leyushko.

00:00:41.657 --> 00:00:45.496
un nokh dem iz geborn gevorn a yingele, vos er hot geheysn Amrem-Yide,

00:00:45.632 --> 00:00:47.479
nokh mayn shver olevasholem.

00:00:48.956 --> 00:00:50.266
un,

00:00:51.636 --> 00:00:53.759
in nayntsn eyn un fertsik

00:00:54.022 --> 00:00:57.710
hot men mikh genumen tsu di ungarishe arbayts batalyon,

00:00:58.135 --> 00:01:02.354
un mayn vayb olehasholem iz gevezn demolts in zibetn monat shvanger.

00:01:03.204 --> 00:01:07.108
un dos drite kind hob ikh keyn mol nisht gezen, zi hot geheysn Malkele,

00:01:07.711 --> 00:01:09.237
ober ikh hob a bild,

00:01:10.755 --> 00:01:14.537
a bil- ikh, ikh hob a PICTURE fun ir, zi iz keyneyn-, z- sh-

00:01:14.581 --> 00:01:15.933
keyn eynhore, UNK,

00:01:16.036 --> 00:01:21.961
zi iz a bild sheyn kind, vi azoy heyst dos, alts, alts lebedik kind hob ikh nisht gehat di skhie tsu zen ir,

00:01:22.351 --> 00:01:24.175
ober vi azoy heyst es shoyn,

00:01:24.265 --> 00:01:28.543
un yo, may- ven ikh bin avekgegan in eyn un fertsik, hob ikh dokh gehat di

00:01:29.355 --> 00:01:31.100
di hirsh-post,

00:01:32.350 --> 00:01:35.965
mayn, dan hob m- hob ikh farlorn di, vi heyst es shoyn,

00:01:36.127 --> 00:01:38.880
az ikh bin gevezn emtlekh UNK, tsu, bay di tshekhn,

00:01:39.091 --> 00:01:41.967
dos hot zikh, dos hobn di ungern oy- avekgenumen,

00:01:42.085 --> 00:01:43.936
azoy az ikh hob nokh gehat di,

00:01:44.198 --> 00:01:47.173
di IBUS hob ikh nokh gehat, ober zi hot,

00:01:47.286 --> 00:01:50.397
zi hot zi, mayn vayb olehasholem hot ober gevolt nokh UNK

00:01:50.522 --> 00:01:53.595
zi hot nokh gehat di meglekhkeyt tsu firn di BUSINESS vayter,

00:01:53.813 --> 00:01:56.838
hot zi gerufn ir shvester fun Tshorne,

00:01:57.504 --> 00:02:02.285
un, me hot zi gerufn Babke, oder zi hot geheysn Nisl, Nisl Leye,

00:02:02.414 --> 00:02:05.813
un zi iz gevezn mit mayn vayb olehasholem, zi hot geholfn

00:02:06.011 --> 00:02:09.481
vayl se iz geborn gevorn dos kind, hot zi geholfn dos kind ertsien,

00:02:11.442 --> 00:02:17.481
un, ober mit di tsayt hot men deys, dey dey dey hirsh-post do, IBUS,

00:02:17.814 --> 00:02:22.530
oykh tsugenumen, azoy az zi hot gemuzt oyfgebn dey, zi hot dokh gevolt ekzistirn,

00:02:23.148 --> 00:02:27.407
hot, iz dos yingele gegangen in kheyder tsu mayn tate olevasholem in Khust,

00:02:28.839 --> 00:02:32.259
di, un mayn vayb olehasholem iz avekgegangen oyf Tshorne,

00:02:32.333 --> 00:02:34.567
un zi hot zikh mitgenumen dos eltste meydele,

00:02:34.582 --> 00:02:38.493
Leyushko, oder Nisl Leye. me hot zi gerufn Leyushko,

00:02:39.097 --> 00:02:43.814
un vider deys deys meydl vos zi iz gekumen helfn far mayn vayb olehasholem,

00:02:43.814 --> 00:02:46.689
hot gehat a shvester, me hot zi gerufn Reyzl,

00:02:46.790 --> 00:02:49.506
un zi hot gevoynt in Guto, in Slovakay.

00:02:50.049 --> 00:02:53.654
zi iz, zi iz geven an almone, geblibn mit dray, ire dray kinder,

00:02:53.732 --> 00:02:57.198
iz gegangen deys meydl, di Babke,

00:02:57.295 --> 00:03:00.018
iz zi gegangen oyf Guto, un zi hot mitgenumen mit zikh

00:03:00.178 --> 00:03:01.765
dos yingste kind mayns.

00:03:02.160 --> 00:03:06.827
nokh dem hot zikh gemakht, in yare fir un fertsik, hot zikh gemakht di getos,

00:03:07.763 --> 00:03:11.938
iz mayn vayb olehasholem geforn oyf Khust oyf peysekh,

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:14.617
un demolts hot zikh gemakht di geto,

00:03:15.094 --> 00:03:18.592
un fun dortn iz zi deportirt gevorn mit mayne eltern,

00:03:19.111 --> 00:03:21.839
un zi hot mitgenumen dos yingele mit zikh,

00:03:23.409 --> 00:03:29.101
SO az in in in geto hot men tsugenumen di, dos, dos ki- dos kind fun ir,

00:03:29.502 --> 00:03:32.913
vayl me hot gezogt az dey, dey v- dey vos zey geyen

00:03:33.251 --> 00:03:37.148
dey velkhe zenen arbayts feik dey, dey geyen tsu di arbet.

00:03:37.817 --> 00:03:42.123
hot zi ahingegebn mayn yingele hot zi ahingegebn far mayne tate mame olehasholem,

00:03:42.476 --> 00:03:45.641
azoy az dos yingele iz nebekh avekgegangen in

00:03:46.259 --> 00:03:48.091
yud dalet,

00:03:49.636 --> 00:03:51.860
vos iz gevezn demolts,

00:03:52.196 --> 00:03:53.570
dalet sivn.

00:03:54.227 --> 00:03:59.999
iz, iz di yortsayt, demolts hot men zey ge- arayngefirt in geto, zey zenen dortn fargazt gevorn.

00:04:00.331 --> 00:04:01.207
in Khust.

00:04:01.209 --> 00:04:03.275
in neyn in, in Oyshvits.

00:04:03.676 --> 00:04:04.465
fun Khust?

00:04:04.315 --> 00:04:06.197
fun Khust hot men zey avekgefirt

00:04:04.465 --> 00:04:06.244
UNK

00:04:06.244 --> 00:04:08.009
vu iz geven di geto?

00:04:07.962 --> 00:04:09.518
in Khust.

00:04:08.890 --> 00:04:12.174
in Khust. vu lang zenen zey geven in geto, veyst ir?

00:04:12.248 --> 00:04:19.156
n- nisht tsu lang, ikh ikh veys, pinktlekh nisht, vayl ikh bin shoyn nisht gevezn dort, vayl ikh hob, ikh bin avekgegangen, mikh hot men avekgefirt oyf oyf Ukraine.

00:04:18.942 --> 00:04:20.892
yo, un fun Khust hot men zey...

00:04:20.841 --> 00:04:23.565
un oyf Khust hot men zey deportirt oyf Oyshvits.

00:04:24.017 --> 00:04:27.551
in erev, a tog far erev yontev,

00:04:27.779 --> 00:04:33.706
far erev shvues, hot men likvidirt, dey, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, dey velkhe zenen gekumen oyf Oyshvits,

00:04:33.900 --> 00:04:36.875
hot men zey gef- bald arayngefirt in

00:04:36.966 --> 00:04:40.797
dey arbayts-feike hot men, hot men SEPARATED, tsu di arbet,

00:04:40.934 --> 00:04:45.410
un dey velkhe zenen nisht gevezn tsu di arbet, nisht feik tsu di arbet, mayn tate mame,

00:04:45.502 --> 00:04:49.235
mit di yingere kinder, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, mayn geshvister,

00:04:49.356 --> 00:04:51.919
hot men, vi azoy heyst es shoyn,

00:04:52.656 --> 00:04:56.283
oykh likvidirt. un s'iz geblibn lebn mayn

00:04:56.671 --> 00:04:59.663
mayn shvester Ester, Etu,

00:05:00.317 --> 00:05:04.527
un Zisl, un Beylu, dey dray zenen gegangen tsu der arbet.

00:05:04.673 --> 00:05:11.642
ober di iberike kinder zenen, zenen arayngefirt in geto, un dort hot men zey likvidirt.

00:05:11.770 --> 00:05:15.370
ober mayn bruder V-, Volvi,

00:05:15.486 --> 00:05:19.351
im hot men gefirt tsu di arbayts batalyon, azoy er iz nisht dort gevezn,

00:05:20.077 --> 00:05:27.573
vider, Shmuel iz, hot men, iz er iz yo deportirt gevorn, ober im hot men geshikt tsu der arbet,

00:05:27.991 --> 00:05:32.422
er iz ge- dort gevezn mit mayn a feter Naftoli, ikh gedenk nokh ven er iz geshtorbn,

00:05:32.603 --> 00:05:35.067
dort vu mayn feter Naftoli iz gevezn,

00:05:35.727 --> 00:05:38.835
vider, Toli,

00:05:39.097 --> 00:05:42.359
iz ergets far- aropgeblibn,

00:05:42.467 --> 00:05:45.885
ober nokh dem hot men, shpeter hobn zey im, hobn zey im gekhapt.

00:05:46.230 --> 00:05:48.427
un ven er iz geshtorbn,

00:05:48.676 --> 00:05:50.734
hot keyner nisht keyn IDEA.

00:05:51.512 --> 00:05:56.008
un dos iz geven in velkhn yor vos men hot zey deportirt keyn AUSCHWITZ?

00:05:54.477 --> 00:05:55.995
in yare fir un fertsik.

00:05:56.701 --> 00:05:59.417
un vos iz geshen mit ayere dray kinder?

00:05:59.417 --> 00:06:00.578
un mit ayer froy?

00:06:00.291 --> 00:06:06.868
yo, iz azoy, mayn mayn froy iz iz nokh avekgegangen mit mayn tatn mit mayn mamen oyf Oyshvits,

00:06:07.067 --> 00:06:09.624
un dort hot men tsugenumen dos yingele fun ir,

00:06:09.788 --> 00:06:16.251
un zey, un zey, me hot zi, men hot zi arayngeshtelt in in gaz kamer me hot zi, me hot zey geharget, fargazt.

00:06:17.545 --> 00:06:21.082
vider mayn vayb olehasholem iz gegangen mit mayn shvester,

00:06:21.793 --> 00:06:23.838
dray shvester,

00:06:24.071 --> 00:06:25.472
Zisl,

00:06:25.722 --> 00:06:30.171
dos heyst Etu, Zisl, un Beylu. zey zenen gegangen tsu di arbet.

00:06:30.341 --> 00:06:33.708
ober Etu hot men genumen, zi hot, arayngeshtelt in di kokh.

00:06:34.289 --> 00:06:37.392
mayn vayb olehasholem hot keyn treyfes nisht gegesn.

00:06:38.411 --> 00:06:43.995
un mayn mayn shvester oleha- zol zayn gezunt, zi vos zi voynt yetst in Vin,

00:06:44.456 --> 00:06:49.049
iz, hot gearbet in di kokh, un zi fleg ir gebn fun di kokh dortn

00:06:49.155 --> 00:06:52.131
esn zey, zi hot keyn treyfes hot zi nisht gegesn,

00:06:52.284 --> 00:06:57.683
hot zi gegebn far ir dortn zol zol, tsu ernern zikh, azoy azoy hot zi ekzistirt.

00:06:57.967 --> 00:07:00.905
un vos iz geshen mit ayere tsvey meydelekh?

00:07:00.863 --> 00:07:02.085
yo, iz azoy...

00:07:02.271 --> 00:07:07.444
dos dos tsveyte kind vos ikh hob gezogt az deys deys dey shvegerin Babke

00:07:07.544 --> 00:07:13.412
iz gegangen tsu ir shvester oyf Guto, dos iz in Slovakay lebn Komurn nisht vayt fun

00:07:13.906 --> 00:07:16.354
nisht vayt fun Presburg,

00:07:16.576 --> 00:07:20.021
zi hot zikh oyfgehaltn bay di shvester, ober mit di tsayt

00:07:19.438 --> 00:07:21.981
dos iz geven di eltste?

00:07:22.001 --> 00:07:23.975
neyn dos iz geven dos yingste,

00:07:23.513 --> 00:07:24.921
di yingste, Malke.

00:07:25.189 --> 00:07:26.461
Malkele, yo.

00:07:26.763 --> 00:07:31.419
SO zi iz deportirt gevorn mit ir shvester vos zi hot gehat dray kinder,

00:07:31.562 --> 00:07:35.752
hot men zey deportirt fun Guto oyf Komurn, dort hot men gemakht a,

00:07:36.532 --> 00:07:39.954
a nisht, nisht keyn CONCENTRATION CAMP, nor a geto.

00:07:40.187 --> 00:07:41.761
un fun dort hot men zey,

00:07:45.557 --> 00:07:48.695
ikh gedenk nisht pinktlekh dem tog, ober ikh hob es oyfgeshribn az UNK

00:07:49.319 --> 00:07:54.942
ober zi iz, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, zi iz, zi hot zikh, men hot zi gevolt tsunemen di kinder,

00:07:55.058 --> 00:07:57.738
fun mayn shvegerin, iz a tsvontsik yerik meydl,

00:07:58.211 --> 00:08:03.062
az zi zol geyn tsu der arbet, un az, un dos meydele zol men araynleygn in vi heyst es shoyn,

00:08:03.283 --> 00:08:07.144
zi hot zikh ober nisht gevolt sheydn fun mayn, fun mayn meydele,

00:08:07.430 --> 00:08:12.408
iz zi oykh gegangen in Oysh- in Oyshvits mit di, un zi dort geven, un fargazt gevorn.

00:08:12.731 --> 00:08:16.610
azoy az zi iz mit ir shvester un un fun, un fun

00:08:17.031 --> 00:08:21.170
fun Komurn hot men, hot men avekgefirt oyf Oyshvits un dortn zenen zey

00:08:21.470 --> 00:08:26.892
likvidirt gevorn. vider mayn eltste meydele iz geforn gehat oyf

00:08:26.993 --> 00:08:30.148
azoy mayn vayb olehasholem zi hot zi hot zikh gevolt ekzistirn,

00:08:30.302 --> 00:08:33.520
iz zi gevorn dort vu ir muter hot gevoynt in Tshorno,

00:08:33.657 --> 00:08:35.863
fun dortn flegn zey forn oyf Pest,

00:08:35.973 --> 00:08:39.975
zi hot gekoyft tekstil un azoy hot zi, men dokh gevolt ekzistirn.

00:08:40.082 --> 00:08:42.575
hot zi gehandlt, zi fleg koyfn in Pest skhoyre,

00:08:42.654 --> 00:08:45.120
un firn oyf Tshorno, azoy in in, tekstil.

00:08:45.395 --> 00:08:49.900
un un dos dos eltste meydele iz geven, ober mayn vayb olehasholem,

00:08:50.199 --> 00:08:55.757
iz yetst fun nokh dem vos se hot zikh gemakht dortn dey dey geto, iz zi nokh gevezn shoyn nokh dem in Khust,

00:08:56.481 --> 00:09:00.352
iz zi iz, zi iz deportirt gevorn fun Khust, mitn mitn mitn yingele,

00:09:00.625 --> 00:09:05.325
un dos, dos dos yingste meydele iz deportirt gevorn mit mayn shvegerin.

00:09:05.479 --> 00:09:08.418
un dos, dos eltste kind iz geblibn

00:09:08.873 --> 00:09:12.232
iz geblibn azoy vi mayn vayb olehasholem iz geforn oyf Khust,

00:09:12.335 --> 00:09:16.535
iz geblibn dos, dos dos eltste kind Leyushko,

00:09:16.652 --> 00:09:18.661
bay di shviger, dos heyst bay ir babe.

00:09:18.806 --> 00:09:23.132
un zi iz fun dortn likvi-, vi heyst es shoyn, geshikt gevorn fun Tshorno,

00:09:23.602 --> 00:09:25.729
oyf,

00:09:26.809 --> 00:09:28.855
 vi hot es geheysn?

00:09:34.329 --> 00:09:35.910
nisht Komurn,

00:09:37.273 --> 00:09:40.239
Shopron! Ernburg.

00:09:40.338 --> 00:09:44.717
fun dortn iz iz zi deportirt gevorn mit mayn ba- mit mayn shviger,

00:09:44.873 --> 00:09:49.923
un zi iz dortn in in geto arayngekumen, un zi, zi hot dokh nisht gehat mit UNK,

00:09:50.077 --> 00:09:56.861
mit vemen tsu geyn, dos heyst es, zi iz gevezn a, a zibn yerik meydele, tsi vifl alt zi iz geven, efsher elter gevezn.

00:09:57.477 --> 00:09:59.112
yo SURE iz zi elter geven.

00:09:59.261 --> 00:10:04.684
un, zi iz, di- zi iz fargazt gevorn mit mayn, mit mayn shviger tsuzamen.

00:10:05.220 --> 00:10:07.418
un vel- vu, in velkhe

00:10:07.418 --> 00:10:08.603
ko- in velkhn

00:10:08.377 --> 00:10:10.806
shivoser betamez, iz es gevezn.

00:10:12.268 --> 00:10:15.813
zi- zibetsn tog in tamez, shivoser,

00:10:14.754 --> 00:10:18.482
no, in in velkhe shtot, in velkhn CAMP iz zi geven?

00:10:18.441 --> 00:10:21.326
fun ven zi, koydem iz zi gevezn in Shopron.

00:10:21.491 --> 00:10:29.310
fun Shopron hot men zi deportirt oyf Oyshvits. in dortn iz zi, vi heyst es shoyn, likvidirt gevorn, mit mayn, mit mayn shviger tsuzamen.

00:10:34.203 --> 00:10:37.590
ikh bin gevoyr gevorn az mayn vayb hot gehat dos drite kind,

00:10:37.795 --> 00:10:39.877
in shoyn in Ukraine.

00:10:40.777 --> 00:10:47.204
vayl tsvey monatn shpeter iz dos kind geborn, ikh hob gebetn me zol mikh aheymlozn, ober men hot mir nisht gegebn keyn urloyb.

00:10:47.446 --> 00:10:52.719
azoy az dos kind hob ikh keyn mol nisht gezen, un nishto mer keyn bild nisht gehat.

00:10:53.810 --> 00:10:59.416
un der arbet batalyon vu ir hot, vu me hot aykh aykh tsugenumen,

00:10:59.416 --> 00:11:01.206
zenen geven nor yidn?

00:11:01.301 --> 00:11:06.812
s'iz gevezn a, nor a yidisher, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, tsvey hundert tsvontsik mentshn hobn bashtanen a COMPANY.

00:11:06.795 --> 00:11:08.980
dos hot ge- gehat a nomen?

00:11:08.902 --> 00:11:14.416
arbayts batalyon hot dos geheysn oyf yidish, ober oyf ungarish hot dos geheysn MUNKASZOLGALATOS,

00:11:14.823 --> 00:11:22.939
un mikh hot men geshikt, se hot geheysn se vet zayn epes a po- a monat tsi dray monatn vi, hot ikh mir mit genumen a

00:11:23.539 --> 00:11:28.365
s'iz gevezn, yud dalet, vi azoy iz iz gevezn? in JUNE!

00:11:28.563 --> 00:11:34.239
hob ikh mir mitgenumen aza laykhtn kots dortn, vos, mit vos ikh zol mikh tsudekn,

00:11:34.396 --> 00:11:37.739
hot men undz avekgefirt oyf oyf Ungver,

00:11:38.034 --> 00:11:42.344
oyf tshekhish hot dos geheysn UZHHOROD, oyf ungerish hot es geheysn UNGVAR,

00:11:43.460 --> 00:11:47.961
un fun dortn hot men undz nokh dem avekgefirt oyf Yasin,

00:11:48.076 --> 00:11:52.096
in Yasin hobn mir gezen dort, di ungern hobn demolts deportirt

00:11:52.269 --> 00:11:55.193
ungarishe yidn, men hot gezogt az zey zenen Polyakn, hot

00:11:55.304 --> 00:11:57.456
hot men zey oysgevizn fun Khust,

00:11:58.066 --> 00:12:01.407
un nisht nor fun Khust, nor ikh meyn fun gants Karpatn Rus,

00:12:01.593 --> 00:12:05.544
un me hot zey avekgefirt, aribergefirt dem Don.

00:12:05.729 --> 00:12:08.301
dort dort dortn lebn lebn

00:12:08.406 --> 00:12:10.630
lebn Kamenets Podolsk.

00:12:10.774 --> 00:12:15.787
undz ze'mir dort durkhgeforn dortn, a, undz ze'mir ariber, geven, undz ze'mir oykhet koydem geforn,

00:12:15.913 --> 00:12:20.577
koydem ze'mir gevezn in Ungvar, un fun Ungvar hot men undz avekgefirt oyf Yasin,

00:12:20.706 --> 00:12:23.181
un fun Yasin hot men undz aribergefirt dem Don,

00:12:24.663 --> 00:12:31.224
un un un oyf, dos iz gevezn, in a fraytik ze'mir durkhgegan Orinyen,

00:12:31.331 --> 00:12:34.510
dos iz a dorf befor Kamenets Podolsk,

00:12:34.613 --> 00:12:36.300
hobn mir dortn getrofn yidn,

00:12:36.419 --> 00:12:39.578
velkhe zenen deportirt gevorn alts poylishe birger,

00:12:39.780 --> 00:12:43.171
un zey hobn undz gezogt az morgn, dos heyst shabes,

00:12:43.278 --> 00:12:50.561
vet men zey ariberfirn, araynfirn oyf Kamenets Podolsk, un fun Kamenets Podolsk vet men zey tsurikfirn oyf Ungarn. ober dos iz gevezn

00:12:50.681 --> 00:12:55.012
a falshe da- zakh, me hot not gevolt az zey zoln zikh ale, zey zoln nisht antloyfn,

00:12:55.149 --> 00:12:57.800
