ze'mir undz oykh ge-, zenen di daytshn gekumen

00:24:52.478 --> 00:24:55.185
vayl zey hobn gemeynt az zey veln zayn gefangen fun di,

00:24:55.968 --> 00:24:58.086
zey veln zayn gefangen fun di,

00:24:59.340 --> 00:25:05.584
di di daytshn hobn moyre gehat az zey veln zayn gefangen fun di rusn, zenen zey gekumen loyfn tsu undzer arbayts batalyon,

00:25:06.016 --> 00:25:10.493
un az undz zoln mir zogn az zey zenen oykh arb- arbayts mentshn.

00:25:11.100 --> 00:25:15.399
azoy az me ho'mir ongehoybn tsu geyn tsu fus durkh Briansker vald.

00:25:15.524 --> 00:25:20.484
gedenk ikh nokh iz gekumen, di rusn hobn bombardirt

00:25:20.747 --> 00:25:24.823
dort vu undz ze'mir gegangen, un nisht vayt fun mir iz gefaln a,

00:25:25.111 --> 00:25:28.453
a bombe, ober se hot undz borekhashem nisht getrofn.

00:25:28.582 --> 00:25:31.355
azoy ze'mir undz durkhgegangen, azoy ze'mir gegangen,

00:25:31.539 --> 00:25:35.678
un v-, ober mit di tsayt hobn zikh di daytshn,

00:25:36.183 --> 00:25:38.681
zenen zey tsu tsu zikh gekumen,

00:25:39.582 --> 00:25:44.645
un un zey hobn gefangen finef un tsvontsik toyznt rusn.

00:25:46.706 --> 00:25:54.065
un nokh dem zey hobn UNK, ze'mir shoyn dortn gegangen tsu fus, ze'mir durkhgegangen di di Briansker vald, un azoy nokh dem nokh dem ze'mir undz vayt-

00:25:54.225 --> 00:25:56.387
Konotop ze'mir ongekumen,

00:25:56.984 --> 00:26:00.201
un dortn ze'mir undz, ho'mir geblibn bay der arbet, un dort...

00:26:00.328 --> 00:26:02.501
vos hot ir dort gemakht, in Konotop?

00:26:02.782 --> 00:26:06.463
me hot, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, di zelbe arbet vos me hot gehat befor, ge-

00:26:06.564 --> 00:26:11.575
geFIXt di di dos, vi heyst es shoyn, di shtrozn.

00:26:11.698 --> 00:26:14.127
un geboyt bunkers.

00:26:14.226 --> 00:26:17.905
vifl, der-, ir dermant zikh vifl s'iz geven

00:26:18.028 --> 00:26:19.584
ungarishe

00:26:19.584 --> 00:26:21.633
soldatn un ofitsirn mit aykh?

00:26:23.050 --> 00:26:24.874
undz ho'mir gehat, vi azoy heyst es shoyn,

00:26:26.167 --> 00:26:30.224
koydem ho'mir undz gehat tsvey komandirn, a leytenant un an ober-leytenant.

00:26:30.683 --> 00:26:32.702
ober di oyberleytenant hobn zey,

00:26:33.105 --> 00:26:38.736
vayl er hot zikh gelozt bash-, s'iz gevezn mentshn vos zey hobn gel- zey hobn gegebn gelt far dem ober-leytenant,

00:26:38.847 --> 00:26:42.117
un er hot zey aribergefirt du- durkhn kam- durkh,

00:26:42.667 --> 00:26:46.293
durkhn Don. er hot zey tsu- tsurik geshvertst keyn Ungarn,

00:26:46.875 --> 00:26:49.824
hot men im nokh dem BESTRAFT un me hot im degradirt.

00:26:50.919 --> 00:26:52.463
un ikh gedenk nokh,

00:26:54.071 --> 00:26:56.725
undz ho'mir, undz ho'mir gearbet gehat in a

00:26:57.556 --> 00:27:00.334
in a, in a, in a shtal.

00:27:01.793 --> 00:27:05.895
un bay nakht bin ikh gegangen, ikh hob genumen a BRUSH, ikh hob mir opgeputst di shikh.

00:27:06.041 --> 00:27:08.961
iz gekumen an ungarisher, POLICE,

00:27:09.824 --> 00:27:13.124
un heybt er on tsu shrayen, " mit di ungerishe,

00:27:13.367 --> 00:27:17.684
vi azoy heyst es shoyn, barsht geystu dir putsn dayne shmutsike shikh?"

00:27:17.913 --> 00:27:21.560
un er hot mikh gerufn tsu, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, nokh dem

00:27:22.964 --> 00:27:24.430
yo, hot er mir gegebn a patsh.

00:27:25.381 --> 00:27:29.413
un er hot mir gezogt ikh zol mikh, zol ikh mikh meldn morgn, vi azoy heyst es shoyn,

00:27:29.880 --> 00:27:35.448
n- az vos ikh hob getun, ikh hob getun a groyse aveyre, ikh hob geputst, vi azoy heyst es shoyn, di shikh mit di, mit dem, mit dem

00:27:35.743 --> 00:27:37.530
di shmutsike shikh mit dem, mit

00:27:37.944 --> 00:27:39.016
hot men undz ge...

00:27:38.287 --> 00:27:40.484
mit vos hot ir geputst di shikh?

00:27:40.359 --> 00:27:43.320
mit dey BRUSH vos me ge, di, geputst di ferd.

00:27:45.348 --> 00:27:49.833
un geyendik, me hot undz gefirt tsu a dokter, vayl men hot undz gevolt BESTRAFn,

00:27:50.366 --> 00:27:55.101
un, tsi, tsi me ken'mir oyshaltn dey dey STRAFE vos di, er vet undz dortn

00:27:55.583 --> 00:27:56.997
fa- farurteyln.

00:27:57.609 --> 00:28:00.898
ho'mir getrofn dem ober-leytenant vos er iz gevezn,

00:28:01.616 --> 00:28:03.904
un vos me hot im degradirt.

00:28:04.673 --> 00:28:11.495
un er hot undz getrofn, me hot undz gefirt tsu di, tsu a dokter zol undz bazukhn, tsi men ken oyshaltn di STRAFE vos me vet undz gebn.

00:28:13.263 --> 00:28:16.750
iz er tsu undz tsugekumen, vu me geyt, hobn mir im gezogt.

00:28:17.376 --> 00:28:19.736
iz er geganen, er hot aroysgenumen gelt,

00:28:20.293 --> 00:28:23.598
un er hot gegebn, er hot gevust az mir esn koshers,

00:28:23.764 --> 00:28:27.080
zogt er deys gelt vos ikh geb enk zolt ets tseteyln

00:28:27.179 --> 00:28:28.835
far di vos esn koshers.

00:28:29.997 --> 00:28:32.960
ir, vi azoy, vi azoy hot er geheysn, ir dermant zikh?

00:28:34.487 --> 00:28:37.998
der er der unterleytenant, er hot geheysn KIRAY,

00:28:39.208 --> 00:28:41.566
un der vos hot aykh gegebn dos gelt?

00:28:40.933 --> 00:28:42.513
gedenk ikh nisht vi azoy er hot geheysn.

00:28:42.745 --> 00:28:44.280
ober er iz geven a Budapester.

00:28:45.341 --> 00:28:49.750
der KIRAY iz, iz nokhn krig hot men im farurteylt,

00:28:50.209 --> 00:28:51.447
men hot im erleydikt.

00:28:52.538 --> 00:28:56.077
vos se iz gevorn mitn andern vey- in Budapest, veys ikh nisht.

00:28:57.433 --> 00:28:59.791
un der nokh vu, vu zent ir hitst

00:28:59.791 --> 00:29:01.507
in vel- velkher,

00:29:01.507 --> 00:29:02.680
shtot zent ir hitst?

00:29:04.005 --> 00:29:05.297
vu ikh halt mit di...

00:29:04.070 --> 00:29:06.836
vu ikh halt, vu halt ir mit di, ye.

00:29:06.645 --> 00:29:10.671
SO me hot, me hot undz avekgefirt gehat dortn, yo mit di tsayt,

00:29:10.804 --> 00:29:14.361
zenen gekumen, nokh dem vi undz ze'mir durkhgegangen di Briansker vald,

00:29:14.993 --> 00:29:17.128
zenen gekumen di,

00:29:17.298 --> 00:29:21.950
di rusn, mit di partizanen, un zey hobn undz dortn,

00:29:23.154 --> 00:29:31.946
vi azoy heyst es shoyn, zey, zey hobn arayn-, di partizanen hobn ayngenumen dortn dey UNK vu ikh bin gevezn, z- es hot geheysn UNK, hot es geheysn.

00:29:31.946 --> 00:29:36.398
tsi heyst es nokh hitstert oykh. al kol ponem. azoy vi dey,

00:29:36.509 --> 00:29:38.539
yo, di regiment undzerer,

00:29:39.057 --> 00:29:41.506
di arbayts batalyon hot gemakht a RÜCKZUG.

00:29:41.800 --> 00:29:45.267
undz ze'mir ober gevezn avekgeshikt fuftsik kilometer,

00:29:45.439 --> 00:29:47.291
mir, mir darfn shteyn blaybn.

00:29:47.391 --> 00:29:47.895
UNK

00:29:47.895 --> 00:29:48.286
shteyn blaybn...

00:29:47.925 --> 00:29:49.192
mitn RÜCKZUG.

00:29:49.220 --> 00:29:49.669
OKAY.

00:29:49.827 --> 00:29:51.007
shteyn blaybn mitn RÜCKZUG.
